================================================================================
Third-Party Architectural Attributions
================================================================================

EGBIMOTO's architecture was informed by patterns and approaches from the
following open-source projects. No source code was copied verbatim; these are
acknowledged as design influences:

- rst-c (Revit Ribbon Profile Manager)
  The Bootstrap + side-engine loading pattern (AssemblyDependencyResolver),
  add-in directory scanning, and health snapshot concepts in EGBIMOTO were
  adapted from this project's architecture.

- pyRevit
  The manifest-driven extension model and operation registry concepts drew
  inspiration from pyRevit's approach to Revit automation.

If any portion of this software is found to incorporate third-party code
subject to its own license terms, those terms apply to that portion and this
NOTICE will be updated accordingly.

